name: StaticBucketMap_removeTest
description: Unit tests for the remove functionality of the StaticBucketMap class.

test_cases.name: testRemoveExistingKey
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of an existing key from the StaticBucketMap.

test_cases.name: testRemoveNonExistingKey
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of a non-existing key from the StaticBucketMap.

test_cases.name: testRemoveFromEmptyMap
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of a key from an empty StaticBucketMap.

test_cases.name: testRemoveHeadOfBucket
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of the head element of a bucket in the StaticBucketMap.

test_cases.name: testRemoveMiddleOfBucket
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of a middle element of a bucket in the StaticBucketMap.

test_cases.name: testRemoveTailOfBucket
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of the tail element of a bucket in the StaticBucketMap.
